title: Digi-Pas DWL3500XY 2-Axis Digital Master Precision Level & Inclinometer with BLUETOOTH, 0.0002”/ft (0.02mm/M) 6 Inch + PRO Software
description: DWL-3500XY is a 2-Axis High Precision Machinist Levels & Inclinometer with built-in Vibrometer, Resolution of 0.001° (0.02mm/M)(0.0002 in/Ft.) and wide measuring range (±20.000°) for levelling, angle, alignment & vibration measurements, and capable of real-time wireless/USB Bluetooth data acquisition & logging.
